1
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:14,700
♪Wander through the bustling world♪

2
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:20,660
♪How could we forget each other?♪

3
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:25,220
♪Indescribable contemplation♪

4
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:33,060
♪Under the bright moon,
I enter the realm of dreams♪

5
00:00:33,340 --> 00:00:38,740
♪Could you be the one in my dreams?♪

6
00:00:39,100 --> 00:00:43,940
♪Only then will I look back with joy♪

7
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:46,820
♪Do you understand? Are you flustered?♪

8
00:00:46,940 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Are you weary? Just let it be a memory♪

9
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:52,180
♪Shall we forget or shall we anticipate?♪

10
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:57,980
♪Either way♪

11
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:08,100
♪My feelings are as tender as summer♪

12
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:21,820
♪Holding hands, I want to see
the four seasons flourish with you♪

13
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:29,780
♪Warming the ends of the earth♪

14
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:38,420
♪Finally, in this boundless world,
everything is under the embrace of longing♪

15
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:46,200
=Blooming Days=

16
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:49,280
=Episode 2=

17
00:01:51,202 --> 00:01:51,961
I don't understand

18
00:01:52,522 --> 00:01:54,482
what you're talking about.

19
00:01:54,482 --> 00:01:55,361
Of course you don't.

20
00:01:56,001 --> 00:01:56,802
If you did,

21
00:01:57,082 --> 00:01:58,601
you wouldn't have been known
as the Idle Young Master.

22
00:01:59,722 --> 00:02:00,241
You...

23
00:02:01,921 --> 00:02:02,402
You...

24
00:02:03,961 --> 00:02:05,281
You're a smart girl.

25
00:02:05,681 --> 00:02:06,881
If I didn't intend to
keep you for my father,

26
00:02:07,641 --> 00:02:09,122
I would've kept you for myself.

27
00:02:09,122 --> 00:02:10,042
Why don't you?

28
00:02:12,601 --> 00:02:14,122
Lu Beiyi can't even make you stay.

29
00:02:14,801 --> 00:02:16,241
Who am I to make you stay?

30
00:02:17,202 --> 00:02:17,881
You love

31
00:02:17,881 --> 00:02:19,122
the man so deeply,

32
00:02:19,562 --> 00:02:20,881
yet parted with him
without batting an eyelid.

33
00:02:21,601 --> 00:02:22,961
Are you seriously ruthless

34
00:02:24,521 --> 00:02:25,202
or

35
00:02:26,042 --> 00:02:26,961
do you have an arrangement?

36
00:02:29,002 --> 00:02:29,842
Stop following me.

37
00:02:33,922 --> 00:02:35,642
What are you doing?

38
00:02:35,881 --> 00:02:36,842
- Go to the mansion.
- Put me down.

39
00:02:36,842 --> 00:02:38,362
- Madam Jinfang.
- It's Lianxiu.

40
00:02:38,402 --> 00:02:39,321
Ms. Qinglian.

41
00:02:39,321 --> 00:02:40,482
Come on, enter.

42
00:02:43,002 --> 00:02:43,681
Lianxiu.

43
00:02:46,762 --> 00:02:47,321
Lianxin.

44
00:02:48,282 --> 00:02:49,482
You're panting heavily.

45
00:02:49,922 --> 00:02:50,681
What are you doing

46
00:02:51,081 --> 00:02:51,961
in broad daylight?

47
00:02:53,081 --> 00:02:53,521
How

48
00:02:54,122 --> 00:02:55,681
did you end up seeing it?

49
00:02:55,961 --> 00:02:57,081
Don't tell a soul.

50
00:03:01,081 --> 00:03:02,002
Since when are you

51
00:03:02,002 --> 00:03:02,842
afraid of your wife?

52
00:03:06,202 --> 00:03:07,681
I don't want any problem.

53
00:03:08,402 --> 00:03:09,241
You get what I mean.

54
00:03:09,482 --> 00:03:11,681
Women are easily jealous.

55
00:03:12,202 --> 00:03:13,282
I don't think all women are like that.

56
00:03:15,002 --> 00:03:16,122
Zhimei isn't.

57
00:03:21,601 --> 00:03:22,762
Lianxin, take care.

58
00:04:00,922 --> 00:04:01,321
Mei'er.

59
00:04:03,562 --> 00:04:04,202
Dear.

60
00:04:10,321 --> 00:04:11,122
How can I let you

61
00:04:11,122 --> 00:04:12,122
do such a menial work?

62
00:04:13,441 --> 00:04:14,441
This is for you.

63
00:04:15,081 --> 00:04:15,801
Give me the thread.

64
00:04:20,161 --> 00:04:20,801
There's no so-called menial work

65
00:04:21,441 --> 00:04:22,522
between us.

66
00:04:23,401 --> 00:04:24,242
Everything about you matters.

67
00:04:56,721 --> 00:04:57,682
Dear, why are you laughing?

68
00:05:00,042 --> 00:05:01,401
I met Lianxin.

69
00:05:02,121 --> 00:05:03,321
In broad daylight

70
00:05:03,802 --> 00:05:04,841
and right outside the mansion,

71
00:05:05,321 --> 00:05:06,281
he simply couldn't wait

72
00:05:06,281 --> 00:05:06,922
to carry a woman

73
00:05:06,922 --> 00:05:07,841
into a carriage.

74
00:05:11,202 --> 00:05:12,161
Since when is Lianxin

75
00:05:12,682 --> 00:05:13,522
so

76
00:05:13,522 --> 00:05:14,482
horny?

77
00:05:14,482 --> 00:05:15,802
He's not that kind of person.

78
00:05:23,161 --> 00:05:24,642
Right outside the mansion?

79
00:05:27,601 --> 00:05:28,561
Did Lady Yao

80
00:05:28,561 --> 00:05:29,482
find a candidater?

81
00:05:31,321 --> 00:05:33,001
No, I must find out.

82
00:05:33,401 --> 00:05:34,242
If this is true,

83
00:05:34,401 --> 00:05:35,321
when the Emperor is granting titles,

84
00:05:35,881 --> 00:05:37,441
he might be appointed as
General of Illustrious Virtue.

85
00:05:38,121 --> 00:05:38,561
Liuyan.

86
00:05:38,841 --> 00:05:40,281
Find the blood nest

87
00:05:40,281 --> 00:05:40,762
from the mansion.

88
00:05:40,762 --> 00:05:41,242
Yes.

89
00:05:45,441 --> 00:05:46,121
Where are you going?

90
00:05:46,401 --> 00:05:47,321
Young Master Xin's mansion.

91
00:05:48,441 --> 00:05:49,522
Are you going there to see the lady

92
00:05:49,522 --> 00:05:50,362
or Lianxin?

93
00:05:56,082 --> 00:05:57,401
Since I've chosen you

94
00:05:57,401 --> 00:05:58,202
as my husband,

95
00:05:58,561 --> 00:05:59,922
the one succeeding the prince

96
00:06:00,082 --> 00:06:01,121
will be none other than you.

97
00:06:01,962 --> 00:06:03,001
Other people

98
00:06:03,362 --> 00:06:04,642
will be my enemies,

99
00:06:04,881 --> 00:06:05,841
including Lianxin.

100
00:06:07,121 --> 00:06:07,561
Hold on.

101
00:06:14,362 --> 00:06:15,001
If you thought

102
00:06:15,001 --> 00:06:16,242
I was the unlikeliest

103
00:06:16,841 --> 00:06:17,522
to succeed my father,

104
00:06:18,522 --> 00:06:19,441
would you still have married me?

105
00:06:31,601 --> 00:06:32,482
Ms. Qinglian.

106
00:06:32,881 --> 00:06:34,082
I'll teach you the way to walk first.

107
00:06:34,682 --> 00:06:35,721
I remember that once,

108
00:06:36,362 --> 00:06:37,642
the prince was busy working.

109
00:06:38,401 --> 00:06:40,561
The princess served him
with snacks and soup.

110
00:06:41,082 --> 00:06:42,841
She went in and out
of Qingkang Hall thrice

111
00:06:43,321 --> 00:06:44,881
yet the prince didn't even notice.

112
00:06:45,561 --> 00:06:47,642
The soup didn't even spill.

113
00:06:48,561 --> 00:06:50,281
The prince used to praise the princess

114
00:06:50,281 --> 00:06:52,242
for walking lightly and elegantly.

115
00:06:53,281 --> 00:06:54,962
All right, let's begin.

116
00:06:55,362 --> 00:06:56,802
Two important points.

117
00:06:57,161 --> 00:06:57,721
Firstly,

118
00:06:59,042 --> 00:07:00,242
make sure the bowl on the tray

119
00:07:00,721 --> 00:07:01,762
doesn't make any sound.

120
00:07:02,401 --> 00:07:03,001
Secondly,

121
00:07:03,841 --> 00:07:05,121
make sure the bell on your feet

122
00:07:05,441 --> 00:07:06,682
doesn't make any sound either.

123
00:07:07,522 --> 00:07:08,042
All right.

124
00:07:08,682 --> 00:07:09,042
Come on.

125
00:07:12,721 --> 00:07:13,682
This is already the sixth.

126
00:07:14,362 --> 00:07:15,482
None of the ladies can sit still.

127
00:07:15,962 --> 00:07:16,682
Other than the prince's legitimate wife

128
00:07:16,682 --> 00:07:17,802
and Lady Ye,

129
00:07:18,161 --> 00:07:19,121
all other ladies have sent
their servants here to find out.

130
00:07:19,642 --> 00:07:21,242
The legitimate wife and Lady Ye

131
00:07:21,242 --> 00:07:22,161
are calm.

132
00:07:23,242 --> 00:07:24,682
Just ignore

133
00:07:24,682 --> 00:07:25,802
the rest.

134
00:07:27,401 --> 00:07:28,561
They try to vie for his attention,

135
00:07:29,721 --> 00:07:30,881
but when my husband has a problem,

136
00:07:31,001 --> 00:07:32,281
few can share the burden.

137
00:07:33,281 --> 00:07:34,281
You're right.

138
00:07:34,682 --> 00:07:36,121
Luckily you're helping him.

139
00:07:36,121 --> 00:07:37,362
Young Master Xin is fortunate.

140
00:07:40,042 --> 00:07:40,601
Ruhua.

141
00:07:42,601 --> 00:07:43,242
Do you think

142
00:07:43,682 --> 00:07:45,001
Lianxin really needs me?

143
00:07:45,601 --> 00:07:48,001
Do you mean Madam Jinfang?

144
00:07:49,881 --> 00:07:50,441
Lady Yao.

145
00:07:50,802 --> 00:07:52,042
Didn't Mr. Xin say?

146
00:07:52,202 --> 00:07:53,362
A few days ago,

147
00:07:53,362 --> 00:07:54,242
Madam Jinfang asked him

148
00:07:54,242 --> 00:07:55,042
for a parrot.

149
00:07:55,281 --> 00:07:56,362
She's returning the favour.

150
00:07:58,401 --> 00:07:59,561
I hope so.

151
00:08:01,121 --> 00:08:02,161
Again.

152
00:08:05,881 --> 00:08:07,762
I'm the daughter of
Ceremony Bureau's Luo Rongyu.

153
00:08:08,001 --> 00:08:08,762
My name is Luo Qinglian.

154
00:08:09,482 --> 00:08:10,281
Greetings, Your Highness.

155
00:08:10,962 --> 00:08:11,522
What did you say?

156
00:08:13,161 --> 00:08:14,321
Did you not eat?

157
00:08:18,242 --> 00:08:20,401
I'm the daughter of
Ceremony Bureau's Luo Rongyu.

158
00:08:20,642 --> 00:08:21,401
My name is Luo Qinglian.

159
00:08:21,401 --> 00:08:22,202
Su Nanchun.

160
00:08:22,601 --> 00:08:23,001
Sir.

161
00:08:23,001 --> 00:08:24,001
What did she have for lunch?

162
00:08:24,321 --> 00:08:25,841
Sir, I think she had beef.

163
00:08:27,401 --> 00:08:29,841
No wonder she sounds like a cow.

164
00:08:31,601 --> 00:08:32,321
Young Master Xin.

165
00:08:32,841 --> 00:08:34,482
You've never met the late princess.

166
00:08:34,482 --> 00:08:36,082
How do you know how she walked

167
00:08:36,082 --> 00:08:36,841
or talked?

168
00:08:37,521 --> 00:08:38,201
Young Master Xin, if you're

169
00:08:38,201 --> 00:08:39,322
trying to find fault with me,

170
00:08:39,721 --> 00:08:40,721
I shall not practise.

171
00:08:43,442 --> 00:08:44,641
Ms. Qinglian is tired.

172
00:08:44,961 --> 00:08:45,882
Take a break.

173
00:08:46,562 --> 00:08:47,482
I'm not.

174
00:08:48,521 --> 00:08:49,281
I feel

175
00:08:49,922 --> 00:08:51,002
chest tightness.

176
00:08:51,401 --> 00:08:53,002
I think this environment is stifling.

177
00:08:53,002 --> 00:08:54,601
I would like to go to
a more spacious one.

178
00:08:55,521 --> 00:08:56,161
No.

179
00:09:01,122 --> 00:09:01,562
Why not?

180
00:09:02,401 --> 00:09:03,122
There's no reason.

181
00:09:04,802 --> 00:09:05,802
In this mansion,

182
00:09:05,882 --> 00:09:07,401
other than Lianxin's Qiege Hall,

183
00:09:08,002 --> 00:09:08,882
my Langyue Hall

184
00:09:08,882 --> 00:09:09,841
is the biggest.

185
00:09:10,841 --> 00:09:11,401
I don't believe

186
00:09:11,401 --> 00:09:12,601
it's not enough for you.

187
00:09:15,721 --> 00:09:16,482
Su Nanchun.

188
00:09:17,362 --> 00:09:18,442
Let's solve a riddle.

189
00:09:20,562 --> 00:09:22,442
Lady Yao, you want me to learn well.

190
00:09:23,042 --> 00:09:23,841
So you must pay attention

191
00:09:23,841 --> 00:09:24,841
to my needs.

192
00:09:25,641 --> 00:09:26,922
I thought it's too hot at noon.

193
00:09:26,922 --> 00:09:28,201
I wanted somewhere with shelter.

194
00:09:28,562 --> 00:09:29,161
You refused.

195
00:09:29,601 --> 00:09:30,802
I feel chest tightness

196
00:09:30,882 --> 00:09:32,322
and want a spacious place.

197
00:09:32,521 --> 00:09:33,562
You still refuse.

198
00:09:33,841 --> 00:09:34,401
What on earth

199
00:09:35,002 --> 00:09:36,081
do you want?

200
00:09:36,482 --> 00:09:37,601
Harbour...

201
00:09:38,201 --> 00:09:39,042
Harbour?

202
00:09:40,802 --> 00:09:42,161
You want to distract us.

203
00:09:44,002 --> 00:09:44,721
An ulterior motive.

204
00:09:46,601 --> 00:09:48,242
An ulterior motive?

205
00:09:50,201 --> 00:09:51,401
Am I right?

206
00:09:52,882 --> 00:09:53,961
You're smart,

207
00:09:54,922 --> 00:09:55,761
but do you know

208
00:09:56,081 --> 00:09:57,042
what gave you away?

209
00:10:00,682 --> 00:10:01,882
No woman

210
00:10:02,562 --> 00:10:03,802
would remain as calm as you

211
00:10:04,641 --> 00:10:05,922
when she parted with a man she loved.

212
00:10:10,761 --> 00:10:11,322
Wishful...

213
00:10:11,922 --> 00:10:12,721
Don't let her escape.

214
00:10:13,721 --> 00:10:14,521
Thinking.

215
00:10:14,841 --> 00:10:16,081
Wishful thinking.

216
00:10:17,042 --> 00:10:17,562
Young Master Xin.

217
00:10:17,802 --> 00:10:20,521
You knew what was going to happen.

218
00:10:23,042 --> 00:10:23,682
Lady Mei!

219
00:10:39,362 --> 00:10:39,802
Girl.

220
00:10:41,042 --> 00:10:42,201
Why are you so careless?

221
00:10:42,882 --> 00:10:43,922
If you injure Lady Mei,

222
00:10:44,281 --> 00:10:45,322
you'll be punished severely.

223
00:10:45,641 --> 00:10:47,562
Lady Mei, spare my life.
I didn't mean it.

224
00:10:47,562 --> 00:10:48,521
Spare my life, Lady Mei.

225
00:10:49,242 --> 00:10:49,922
You may rise.

226
00:10:59,161 --> 00:11:00,042
Lady Mei,

227
00:11:00,961 --> 00:11:02,562
you're usually the most well-behaved.

228
00:11:03,201 --> 00:11:04,922
You barged into Langyue Hall.

229
00:11:05,601 --> 00:11:07,122
It's kind of inappropriate.

230
00:11:10,401 --> 00:11:12,362
Lianxiu just got some blood nest.

231
00:11:12,362 --> 00:11:13,161
I specially brought it here

232
00:11:13,161 --> 00:11:14,442
for you to try it.

233
00:11:14,601 --> 00:11:15,641
So I was in a rush.

234
00:11:17,521 --> 00:11:18,081
What's the matter?

235
00:11:19,761 --> 00:11:20,641
Lady Yao, aren't you inviting me

236
00:11:20,641 --> 00:11:21,521
to go to your place?

237
00:11:23,081 --> 00:11:24,322
Thanks for the blood nest.

238
00:11:24,521 --> 00:11:25,721
Lady Mei, please go back.

239
00:11:27,562 --> 00:11:28,081
Ruhua.

240
00:11:28,081 --> 00:11:28,721
I think

241
00:11:29,201 --> 00:11:30,641
I should put the bird nest

242
00:11:30,641 --> 00:11:31,601
inside the house.

243
00:11:33,641 --> 00:11:34,081
You...

244
00:11:47,922 --> 00:11:48,482
Lianxin.

245
00:11:51,161 --> 00:11:52,362
Why didn't you tell me you're here?

246
00:12:08,322 --> 00:12:10,002
My father missed the Emperor.

247
00:12:10,802 --> 00:12:12,362
He built this mansion

248
00:12:13,242 --> 00:12:14,601
following the design of
our house in the hometown.

249
00:12:15,761 --> 00:12:17,841
When I grew up and had my own mansion,

250
00:12:18,281 --> 00:12:21,281
he gave me this mansion

251
00:12:22,242 --> 00:12:23,201
as my official residence.

252
00:12:24,442 --> 00:12:25,161
It's beautiful.

253
00:12:26,521 --> 00:12:28,201
When the lotus blooms,

254
00:12:28,961 --> 00:12:29,922
it'll surely be more beautiful.

255
00:12:31,242 --> 00:12:32,601
What is the pond called?

256
00:12:43,242 --> 00:12:44,081
Weixi Pond.

257
00:12:45,161 --> 00:12:46,201
Weixi Pond?

258
00:12:51,242 --> 00:12:51,841
That's right.

259
00:12:52,961 --> 00:12:53,882
This pond

260
00:12:55,122 --> 00:12:56,322
was built for you.

261
00:13:06,081 --> 00:13:07,201
There's so much reed by the river.

262
00:13:08,961 --> 00:13:09,922
There's still dew.

263
00:13:11,882 --> 00:13:12,961
Where's the woman of my dreams?

264
00:13:15,242 --> 00:13:16,322
She's on the bank.

265
00:13:19,002 --> 00:13:20,042
Back when my father

266
00:13:20,281 --> 00:13:21,521
gave me the mansion,

267
00:13:21,641 --> 00:13:22,882
the first thing I did

268
00:13:22,882 --> 00:13:24,242
was building this pond.

269
00:13:25,721 --> 00:13:26,961
It's over.

270
00:13:28,562 --> 00:13:29,882
You shouldn't have brought it up.

271
00:13:30,242 --> 00:13:30,761
Yes.

272
00:13:31,482 --> 00:13:32,961
It's over. I shouldn't
have brought it up.

273
00:13:33,161 --> 00:13:35,562
After all, you're married
to my fourth brother.

274
00:13:35,922 --> 00:13:36,802
I just didn't expect

275
00:13:36,802 --> 00:13:37,641
that my first time bringing you here

276
00:13:37,641 --> 00:13:38,721
would be an act to guard against you.

277
00:13:42,961 --> 00:13:44,281
Guard against me?

278
00:13:45,242 --> 00:13:47,281
You knew I would come.

279
00:13:47,721 --> 00:13:49,081
So you waited for me

280
00:13:49,081 --> 00:13:49,721
at Langyue Hall.

281
00:13:52,081 --> 00:13:53,401
How would I know?

282
00:13:54,281 --> 00:13:55,442
You met Lianxiu

283
00:13:55,442 --> 00:13:56,482
at Hongyan Gate.

284
00:13:57,081 --> 00:13:58,601
You knew he'd tell me.

285
00:14:00,922 --> 00:14:02,281
I don't understand.

286
00:14:02,761 --> 00:14:03,641
Do you even know me well

287
00:14:03,641 --> 00:14:04,482
or not?

288
00:14:04,761 --> 00:14:06,601
