but why?

380
00:20:58,962 --> 00:21:00,562
Why are you avoiding me, too?

381
00:21:02,082 --> 00:21:04,361
Snowball, come out, please.

382
00:21:04,802 --> 00:21:05,881
I'll give you fish.

383
