395
00:21:33,641 --> 00:21:34,322
Why?

396
00:21:35,001 --> 00:21:36,042
Isn't this a nice place?

397
00:21:36,161 --> 00:21:37,401
Don't I treat it well?

398
00:21:37,962 --> 00:21:38,881
It's nice here,

399
00:21:39,881 --> 00:21:40,922
