403
00:21:46,082 --> 00:21:47,281
How do you know

404
00:21:47,281 --> 00:21:48,361
I'm the prince's son?

405
00:21:54,722 --> 00:21:55,722
The more privileged you are,

406
00:21:56,881 --> 00:21:57,962
the simpler your demands are.

407
00:22:00,481 --> 00:22:01,281
Kids of ordinary families

408
00:22:01,281 --> 00:22:02,481
might be happier than you.

409
00:22:11,641 --> 00:22:13,442
