410
00:22:13,722 --> 00:22:15,641
No, I'm not looking for it.

411
00:22:16,202 --> 00:22:17,481
Since I like Snowball,

412
00:22:18,082 --> 00:22:18,842
I should let it

413
00:22:18,842 --> 00:22:20,161
