414
00:22:20,802 --> 00:22:22,281
I want to let you out.

415
00:22:22,682 --> 00:22:24,042
You've been confined.

416
00:22:24,042 --> 00:22:25,281
You must be unhappy, too.

417
00:22:30,361 --> 00:22:30,842
Hui'er.

418
00:22:31,761 --> 00:22:32,562
What are you doing?

419
00:22:33,202 --> 00:22:35,241
Father, I want to let her out.

420
00:22:35,602 --> 00:22:36,682
You don't have to.

421
00:22:36,922 --> 00:22:38,641
She's leaving tomorrow.

422
00:22:38,722 --> 00:22:39,241
Seriously?

423
00:22:40,442 --> 00:22:40,922
Come here.

424
00:22:43,241 --> 00:22:44,521
Have fun over there.

425
00:22:44,761 --> 00:22:46,401
I need to talk to the lady.

426
00:22:46,401 --> 00:22:46,842
All right.

427
00:23:03,001 --> 00:23:04,802
Young Master Xin, you're good

428
