434
00:23:17,001 --> 00:23:17,521
Girl.

435
00:23:21,442 --> 00:23:22,202
Can you read?

436
00:23:23,161 --> 00:23:23,761
Take a look.

437
00:23:24,202 --> 00:23:24,842
Come on.

438
00:23:30,241 --> 00:23:31,361
