442
00:23:36,761 --> 00:23:38,401
Lu Beiyi participated in
the examination in secret.

443
00:23:39,481 --> 00:23:40,281
Impossible.

444
00:23:41,001 --> 00:23:42,121
He doesn't like it.

445
00:23:42,521 --> 00:23:43,082
Why...

446
00:23:43,401 --> 00:23:44,361
He likes it.

447
00:23:45,121 --> 00:23:45,881
