448
00:23:45,962 --> 00:23:47,641
because you didn't like it.

449
00:23:50,602 --> 00:23:52,121
It's the best article

450
00:23:52,121 --> 00:23:53,241
in this examination.

451
00:23:53,842 --> 00:23:55,401
