452
00:23:55,401 --> 00:23:56,202
apart from

453
00:23:57,001 --> 00:23:58,042
his abundant talent?

454
00:24:00,082 --> 00:24:01,202
Yearning.

455
00:24:02,161 --> 00:24:03,881
Yearning for fame and fortune.

456
00:24:04,442 --> 00:24:05,922
I've never met anyone else

457
00:24:06,202 --> 00:24:07,881
