458
00:24:08,842 --> 00:24:09,842
Do you seriously believe

459
00:24:10,802 --> 00:24:13,001
he'll give up for good?

460
00:24:23,481 --> 00:24:24,722
Since I like Snowball,

461
00:24:24,802 --> 00:24:25,682
I should let it

462
00:24:25,682 --> 00:24:26,962
do what it wants to do.

463
00:24:30,161 --> 00:24:30,802
I shall

464
00:24:30,802 --> 00:24:31,682
pursue fame and fortune with him then.

465
00:24:31,962 --> 00:24:32,881
