478
00:25:04,641 --> 00:25:06,001
Don't tell me you feel bad now.

479
00:25:13,922 --> 00:25:15,082
Go to bed, girl.

480
00:26:09,602 --> 00:26:11,401
I'm Luo Qinglian.

481
00:26:11,922 --> 00:26:12,881
Greetings, Your Highness.

482
00:26:16,641 --> 00:26:17,481
Your temperament

483
00:26:18,802 --> 00:26:19,641
and mannerism

484
00:26:21,521 --> 00:26:23,562
