488
00:26:35,202 --> 00:26:35,562
Come on.

489
00:26:38,202 --> 00:26:40,361
I'll return to the mansion today, too.

490
00:26:40,802 --> 00:26:41,682
Ms. Qinglian,

491
00:26:41,842 --> 00:26:42,922
