501
00:27:23,042 --> 00:27:23,881
Over the years,

502
00:27:26,842 --> 00:27:27,922
I've witnessed

503
00:27:27,922 --> 00:27:29,442
the prince's love and longing.

504
00:27:30,401 --> 00:27:32,881
Since his youth,

505
00:27:33,842 --> 00:27:35,761
he has never forgotten Ms. Fu.

506
00:27:36,521 --> 00:27:37,161
