548
00:31:51,202 --> 00:31:51,722
No.

549
00:31:52,962 --> 00:31:53,682
Something bad happened.

550
00:31:55,322 --> 00:31:56,042
What happened?

551
00:31:58,802 --> 00:31:59,442
Lady Yao.

552
00:31:59,442 --> 00:32:00,361
Something bad happened.

553
00:32:01,281 --> 00:32:02,042
