568
00:32:31,042 --> 00:32:32,322
Mr. Yuan, Chief Clerk of the Right.

569
00:32:33,082 --> 00:32:34,241
Good.

570
00:32:36,602 --> 00:32:37,361
Go to him at once.

571
00:32:37,641 --> 00:32:38,562
Tell my husband

572
00:32:38,562 --> 00:32:40,281
to go along with Mr. Yuan.

573
00:32:42,922 --> 00:32:43,602
Mr. Li.

574
00:32:44,082 --> 00:32:44,922
Are you also here

575
00:32:44,922 --> 00:32:45,962
for the ladies' incident?

576
00:32:45,962 --> 00:32:46,761
That's right.

577
00:32:46,761 --> 00:32:48,401
Since the prince came to Quliang,

578
00:32:48,401 --> 00:32:49,202
such a crazy thing

579
00:32:49,202 --> 00:32:50,361
